<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Friedrich von Kemnat zu Lutzmannstein, Pfleger zu Helfenberg</head><p>Der Rat teilt mit, dass er dem Adressaten in aufrichtiger Weise geschrieben hat, versichert die Freundschaft und verweist auf den Rechtsweg an den üblichen Gerichtsstätten.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_143" id="70v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_143_r2l1"><expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>kemnat<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒu leẅcʒmanſtein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_143_r2l2">pfleger ʒu helffemberg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_143_r2l3"><expan>Vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt beuor . <expan>Frıdr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Kemnater als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt wıe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_143_r2l4"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> ſchrıft dıe wir eẅch nehſt getan <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . niht auf gleıche antwurt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_143_r2l5">ſtee . vnd ſchreıbt <expan>ſunderl<ex>ich</ex></expan> wıe Jr <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>porgen</expan> <expan>ſchreıbe<ex>n</ex></expan> niht <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_143_r2l6">verſteen könnet . Denn auf <expan>eine<ex>n</ex></expan> aufſacʒ etc / Das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol ver </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_143_r2l7"><expan>nom<ex>m</ex>en</expan> / Vnd <expan>meyne<ex>n</ex></expan> daʒ wır <expan>ſölıch<ex>er</ex></expan> ſchrıft pıllıch von eẅch <expan>v<ex>er</ex>tragen</expan> <expan>w<ex>er</ex>en</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_143_r2l8">wan wır <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> eẅch doch nehſt lawter <expan>geſchrıbe<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd <expan>ſchreıbe<ex>n</ex></expan> eẅch das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_143_r2l9">yecʒ aber / Daʒ wır noch ʒu dıſen <expan>ʒeıte<ex>n</ex></expan> mıt eẅch niht <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> wıſſen ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_143_r2l10"><expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> denn guts / Auch wıſſen wır nıht wer dıe <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> ſınd . ſo </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_143_r2l11"><expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> wır auch ʒu dıſen <expan>ʒeıt<ex>en</ex></expan> nıht ſache . <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> wır rechts von eẅch be = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_143_r2l12">dürffen Deẅht eẅch <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> . daʒ Jr <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒu vns ıcht <expan>ʒuſpreche<ex>n</ex></expan> hettet ſo </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_143_r2l13"><expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır eẅch auch / <expan>freẅntl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> <expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ſein an den <expan>ſtette<ex>n</ex></expan> da wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_143_r2l14">das denn <expan>pıllıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> tun <expan>ſüll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_143" id="70v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>Kemnat<ex>er</ex></expan> zu Lewczmanstein, pfleger zu
                        Helffemberg</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Uns<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst bevor.
                                                  <expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Kemnater, als ir
                                                uns <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt, wie
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> schrift, die wir
                                                ewch nehst getan <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, niht
                                                auf gleiche antwurt stee, und schreibt
                                                  <expan>sunderl<ex>ich</ex></expan>, wie ir
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>porgen</expan>
<expan>schreibe<ex>n</ex></expan> niht
                                                  <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> versteen könnet,
                                                denn auf <expan>eine<ex>n</ex></expan> aufsacz etc.,
                                                das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                                                  <expan>vernom<ex>m</ex>en</expan> und
                                                  <expan>meyne<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz wir
                                                  <expan>sölich<ex>er</ex></expan> schrift pillich
                                                von ewch <expan>v<ex>er</ex>tragen</expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>en</expan>, wan wir
                                                  <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ewch doch nehst
                                                lawter <expan>geschribe<ex>n</ex></expan> und
                                                  <expan>schreibe<ex>n</ex></expan> ewch das yecz,
                                                aber daz wir noch zu disen
                                                  <expan>zeite<ex>n</ex></expan> mit ewch niht
                                                  <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> wissen zu
                                                  <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, denn guts. Auch
                                                wissen wir niht, wer die
                                                  <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> sind. So
                                                  <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan> wir auch zu disen
                                                  <expan>zeit<ex>en</ex></expan> niht sache,
                                                  <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> wir rechts von ewch
                                                bedürffen. Dewht ewch <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>,
                                                daz ir <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> zu uns icht
                                                  <expan>zu spreche<ex>n</ex></expan> hettet, so
                                                  <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir ewch auch
                                                  <expan>frewntl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> sein an den
                                                  <expan>stette<ex>n</ex></expan>, da wir das denn
                                                  <expan>pillich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> tun
                                                  <expan>süll<ex>e</ex>n</expan>.
                                                  <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                                                  <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
